Confidence Thresholds

Suggested thresholds:

Confidence	Meaning
>0.92	High-confidence duplicate
0.82–0.92	Strong review candidate
0.70–0.82	Weak overlap
<0.70	Ignore

Thresholds may be adjusted dynamically.

⸻

Quality Validation

Before generating final workbook verify:

1. Every journey appears exactly once.
2. No journey exists in multiple final clusters.
3. Every cluster has a unique ID.
4. Every merge target is unique.
5. Every merge lineage is preserved.
6. Workbook formatting is applied.
7. Workbook is business-review-ready.
8. Intermediate artifacts are persisted.
9. Final mapping sheet is internally consistent.

⸻

