* total clusters
* recommended removals
* recommended merges
* estimated reduction opportunity
* largest overlap groups
* assumptions and ambiguities

⸻

Important Constraints

Do NOT:

* force all clusters into one survivor
* over-merge generic journeys
* assume semantic similarity means equivalence
* delete journeys automatically

The AI is assisting business rationalization.

Humans own the final taxonomy decisions.
